because%20of%20my%20own%20childhood%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20house%2C%20we%20do%20sleepovers%20because%20my%20parents%20never%20let%20me.%20They%20had%20all%20the%20concerns%20I%20listed%20above%2C%20and%20several%20more%20I%20likely%20don't%20remember.%20When%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20hang%20out%20at%20a%20friend's%20house%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20I%20always%20got%20picked%20up%20by%20bedtime.%20I%20remember%20leaving%20birthday%20parties%20hours%20earlier%20than%20the%20other%20girls%2C%20or%20as%20I%20liked%20to%20call%20it%2C%20the%20real%20party%20time.%20I%20called%20it%20this%20because%20the%20girls%20would%20tell%20me%20later%20about%20what%20happened%20after%20I'd%20left.%20Janelle%20prank-called%20Emily's%20crush.%20Jill's%20mom%20yelled%20at%20them%20for%20playing%20tag%20in%20the%20basement.%20Amanda%20learned%20she%20would%20marry%20Joey%20during%20a%20two-hour%20round%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Flife%2F2023%2F05%2F08%2Fhow-play-mash-games-rules%2F10847560002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMASH%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20popular%20fortune-telling%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20an%20adult%2C%20these%20silly%20stories%20may%20sound%20like%20I%20didn't%20miss%20much%2C%20but%20I%20believe%20that%20not%20getting%20to%20participate%20eventually%20led%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firl-social-startups-combat-loneliness-among-millennials-gen-z-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eisolation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20simply%20had%20no%20way%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20my%20friends'%20inside%20jokes%20and%20the%20intense%20bond%20they%20forged%20in%20the%20wee%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%20after%20enjoying%20too%20many%20Twizzlers.%20At%20first%2C%20they%20always%20begged%20me%20to%20stay%20and%20even%20offered%20to%20ask%20my%20mom%20for%20me%2C%20but%20after%20a%20few%20times%2C%20this%20stopped.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20invites%20dried%20up%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D