ng%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20better%20than%20anyone%20else%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20find%20deals%20that%20will%20work%20in%20any%20sort%20of%20interest-rate%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpend%20the%20time%20to%20educate%20yourself%20and%20understand%20all%20about%20what%20the%20occupancy%20rates%20are%2C%20what%20the%20lease%20rates%20are%2C%20what%20the%20building%20purchase%20price%20is%2C%20what%20the%20current%20cap%20rates%20could%20be%2C%20what%20your%20cash%20out%20opportunity%20looks%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barker%2C%20who%20leaned%20on%20research%20early%20in%20his%20real%20estate%20career%20before%20he%20had%20any%20of%20his%20own%20capital%20to%20work%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20particularly%20important%20numbers%20to%20understand%3A%20The%20average%20rent%20rate%20%E2%80%94%20what%20you%20could%20bring%20in%20each%20month%20in%20rental%20income%20%E2%80%94%20and%20your%20monthly%20expenses%2C%20beyond%20your%20mortgage%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20all%20tied%20up%20about%20these%20interest%20rates%20being%206.5%25%2C%207%25%2C%26quot%3B%20Barker%20said.%20%26quot%3BWho%20cares%20what%20the%20interest%20rate%20is%3F%20If%20your%20rent%20roll%20is%20greater%20than%20your%20debt%20service%2C%20and%20you%20can%20still%20keep%20the%20margins%20and%20growth%20you're%20looking%20for%2C%20do%20we%20really%2C%20truly%20want%20to%20get%20tied%20up%20in%20the%20minutia%20of%20percentage%20of%20interest%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20focus%20on%20rates%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20have%20to%20just%20do%20the%20homework%20and%20spend%20a%20little%20time%20to%20reverse%20engineer%20stuff%2C%20think%20about%20pricing%2C%20and%20think%20about%20'what%20is%20the%20opportunity%3F'%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20other%20people%20see%20a%20lack%20of%20opportunity%2C%20a%20different%20lens%20could%20probably%20see%20some%20opportunity%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarker%2C%20who's%20scaled%20to%20more%20than%2030%20commercial%20and%20residential%20properties%2C%20sees%20opportunity%20in%20a%20high-interest%20rate%20environment.%20There%20tends%20to%20be%20less%20competition.%20Plus%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20the%20interest%20rates%20are%20high%2C%20values%20are%20down%2C%20especially%20in%20commercial%20real%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2227029086-5301-4782-b750-eeb521b328c3%5C%22%3EThink%20about%20the%20bigger%20picture%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20multiple%20ways%20to%20build%20wealth%20via%20real%20estate%2C%20beyond%20rental%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20top%20advantages%20real%20estate%20investing%20has%20over%20stock%20market%20investing%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20that%20you%20can%20borrow%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20from%20a%20mortgage%20lender%20to%20buy%20the%20asset%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20share%20any%20of%20the%20appreciation%20with%20your%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20say%20you%20put%2010%25%20down%20on%20a%20%241%20million%20home%2C%20meaning%20you're%20paying%20%24100%2C000%20upfront%20and%20borrowing%20%24900%2C000%20from%20your%20lender.%20If%20the%20house%20goes%20up%2010%25%20in%20value%2C%20it's%20now%20worth%20%241.1%20million%2C%20meaning%20you've%20made%20%24100%2C000.%20It's%20all%20yours.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20share%20it%20with%20your%20lender%2C%20even%20though%20they%20fronted%20you%20%24900%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20real%20estate%20investors%20like%20to%20call%20levered%20appreciation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20money%20the%20bank%20puts%20in%20is%20irrelevant.%20What%20matters%20is%20how%20much%20you%20personally%20have%20to%20put%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barker%2C%20providing%20another%20example%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20buy%20a%20house%20for%20%24200%2C000%2C%20and%20you%20sell%20it%20for%20%24300%2C000.%20What%20do%20your%20friends%20tell%20you%3F%20'I%20made%20%24100%2C000.'%20Fair%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20let's%20say%20you%20only%20put%2010%25%20down%20on%20the%20property%2C%20so%20you're%20out%20of%20pocket%20%2420%2C000%2C%20he%20added.%20That%20means%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20took%20%2420%2C000%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20%24100%2C000.%20You%205%20times-ed%20your%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lower%20you%20can%20keep%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20you're%20personally%20putting%20in%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20higher%20the%20multiple%20goes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20puzzle%20to%20solve%20then%20becomes%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20do%20you%20personally%20have%20to%20come%20to%20the%20table%20with%20to%20get%20the%20asset%20that%20gives%20you%20the%20return%20you're%20looking%20for%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-real-estate-investor-explains-why-high-rates-dont-matter-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750930202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c6d893d5881a51c1c189a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-real-estate-investor-explains-why-high-rates-dont-matter-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BQuit%20worrying%20about%20interest%20rates%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20investor%20and%20entrepreneur%20Jeremy%20Barker.%20Instead%2C%20focus%20on%20what%20you%20can%20control.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-real-estate-investor-explains-why-high-rates-dont-matter-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20stand%20for%20what%20I%20believe'%3A%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20judicial%20nominee%20denies%20advising%20lawyers%20to%20ignore%20court%20orders%3B%20amid%20whistleblower%20complaint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750930118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22ht