ef%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-weak-ipo-ai-skepticism-nvidia-gpu-neocloud-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%20computing%20company%20Coreweave%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20seen%20their%20shares%20soar%20after%20their%20IPOs%2C%20signaling%20renewed%20investor%20appetite%20for%20new%20listings%20across%20industries.%20CoreWeave's%20stock%20has%20climbed%20over%20330%25%20since%20its%20March%20debut%2C%20while%20Circle's%20stock%20has%20exploded%20more%20than%20630%25%20since%20its%20early%20June%20IPO%2C%20as%20of%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20Hinge%20Health%20and%20Omada%20Health%20have%20gone%20public%2C%20venture-backed%20digital%20health%20startups%20can%20breathe%20easier%20knowing%20IPOs%20are%20on%20the%20table%20again%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstakes-for-healthcare-ipo-are-higher-than-ever-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efew%20late-stage%20healthcare%20startups%20with%20the%20right%20financial%20profiles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20and%20kick%20off%20more%20official%20IPO%20preparations%20if%20they're%20otherwise%20ready%20to%20exit.%20But%20facing%20those%20high%20standards%20for%20public%20healthcare%20companies%2C%20continued%20market%20uncertainties%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20preparation%20required%20for%20a%20public%20market%20debut%20most%20healthcare%20IPO%20hopefuls%20are%20targeting%20exits%20in%202026%20or%20later%2C%20investors%2C%20bankers%2C%20and%20analysts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithin%20the%20next%2012%20to%2018%20months%2C%20I%20think%20we're%20likely%20to%20see%20more%20listings.%20Whether%20that%20happens%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20I'm%20not%20convinced%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aaron%20DeGagne%2C%20a%20senior%20healthcare%20analyst%20at%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6e08dd5-e252-4a7b-a2c3-bce785c46cef%5C%22%3EThe%20long%20road%20to%20IPO%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20expect%20the%20return%20of%20digital%20health%20IPOs%20to%20trigger%20a%20stampede%20of%20public%20market%20debuts%2C%20since%20healthcare%20startups%20haven't%20seen%20a%20receptive%20IPO%20market%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20companies%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20waiting%20to%20make%20their%20debut%20since%20the%20last%20IPO%20window%20closed%20in%202022.%20Hinge%20Health%2C%20which%20went%20public%20last%20month%2C%20told%20CNBC%20after%20its%20%24300%20million%20Series%20D%20raise%20in%202021%20that%20the%20musculoskeletal%20company%20hoped%20to%20go%20public%20as%20early%20as%202022.%20Care%20navigation%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincluded-health-formerly-grand-rounds-ipo-2022-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIncluded%20Health%20had%20also%20been%20targeting%20an%20early%202022%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BI%20reported%20back%20in%202021%3B%20CEO%20Owen%20Tripp%20confirmed%20in%20January%20that%20the%20company%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fincluded-health-formerly-grand-rounds-ipo-2022-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfidentially%20filed%20its%20S-1%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%20in%20preparation.%20Included%20Health%20hasn't%20yet%20exited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20lineup%20of%20healthcare%20companies%20weighing%20their%20exit%20options%20against%20market%20instabilities%20can't%20just%20go%20public%20on%20a%20dime%20whennow%20that%20the%20IPO%20window%20appears%20to%20be%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20startup%20has%20decided%20to%20begin%20the%20official%20process%20to%20go%20public%2C%20Stowe%20said%2C%20the%20work%20involved%20to%20get%20to%20the%20IPO%20date%20will%20take%20at%20least%20six%20months.%20The%20total%20planning%20and%20preparation%20usually%20requires%20a%20year%20or%20more%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20companies%20that%20waited%20for%20Hinge%20Health%20and%20Omada%20Health's%20debuts%20to%20launch%20their%20own%20IPO%20processes%2C%20that%20means%20the%20earliest%20they%20could%20likely%20go%20public%20would%20be%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227097%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hinge%20Health%20cofounders%20Daniel%20Perez%2C%20CEO%2C%20and%20Gabriel%20Mecklenburg%2C%20executive%20chairman.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67eef38db8b41a9673fc9b55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224731%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHinge%20Health's%20cofounders%2C%20executive%20chairman%20Gabriel%20Mecklenburg%20and%20CEO%20Daniel%20Perez.%20The%20musculoskeletal%20care%20provider%20was%20the%20first%20digital%20health%20company%20to%20go%20public%20this%20year.%3Cp%3EHinge%20Health%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20some%20market%20uncertainties%20remain%20that%20could%20leave%20healthcare%20companies%20uneasy%20and%20delay%20their%20IPO%20efforts.%20Stowe%20said%20public%20investors%20continue%20to%20shy%20away%20from%20businesses%20that%20could%20be%20exposed%20to%20tariffs%20in%20the%20face%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20shifting%20tariff%20policies.%20That%20could%20further%20push%20back%20IPOs%20for%20companies%20like%20Medline%2C%20a%20medical%20supply%20maker%20that%20manufactures%20many%20products%20in%20China.%20Medline%20confidentially%20filed%20its%20S-1%20to%20go%20public%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Cheatham%2C%20partner%20and%20head%20of%20healthcare%20and%20life%20sciences%20at%20Breyer%20Capital%2C%20said%20he's%20not%20aware%20of%20any%20healthcare%20startups%20in%20the%20IPO%20pipeline%20for%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20said%20he%20expects%20lots%20of%20M%26amp%3BA%20activity%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20as%20startups%20that%20aren't%20IPO-ready%20but%20are%20looking%20for%20an%20exit%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20lifeline%20%E2%80%94%20try%20to%20get%20bought%20or%20merge%20with%20a%20competitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20lots%20of%20companies%20having%20this%20conversation%20in%20the%20boardrooms%20right%20now%3A%20roll%20or%20be%20rolled%2C%26quot%3B%20Cheatham%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c56bbae6-dc3e-4d94-b554-d7b59f3d6884%5C%22%3EStandards%20still%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20some%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20IPO%20window%20cracked%20open%2C%20not%20every%20healthcare%20company%20hoping%20to%20go%20public%20is%20positioned%20to%20step%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20companies%20that%20are%20very%20good%20IPO%20candidates%20right%20now%20are%20still%20a%20smaller%20subset%20than%20what%20you%20saw%20four%20or%20five%20years%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Barclays'%20Stowe.%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20earlier-stage%2C%20pre-profitability%20businesses%2C%20that's%20a%20much%20harder%20conversation%20across%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstakes-for-healthcare-ipo-are-higher-than-ever-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProfitability%20remains%20a%20key%20concern%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20investors%2C%20a%20standard%20that%20even%20the%20strongest%20IPO%20candidates%20can't%20always%20meet.%20Omada%20Health%20continues%20to%20report%20losses%2C%20including%20a%20net%20loss%20of%20%249.4%20million%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20that%20aren't%20profitable%20may%20need%20to%20compromise%20further%20on%20valuation%20so%20their%20stock%20doesn't%20trade%20down%2C%20PitchBook's%20DeGagne%20said.%20While%20Omada%20Health's%20stock%20popped%20when%20it%20went%20public%20at%20a%20%241.1%20billion%20valuation%2C%20roughly%20flat%20with%20its%20last%20private%20valuation%20of%20over%20%241%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20the%20company%20saw%20its%20shares%20begin%20to%20decline%20in%20the%20days%20after%20its%20IPO%20in%20early%20June.%20As%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20its%20market%20cap%20sits%20at%20%24875%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20startups%20across%20the%20board%20are%20already%20being%20forced%20to%20make%20significant%20valuation%20concessions%20to%20go%20public.%20While%20Hinge%20Health%20is%20profitable%20and%20reported%20more%20than%20double%20Omada%20Health's%20revenue%20last%20year%2C%20its%20%242.6%20billion%20IPO%20valuation%20represented%20a%2058%25%20markdown%20from%20its%20last%20private%20valuation%20of%20%246.2%20billion%2C%20notched%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHinge%20Health's%20stock%20has%20climbed%20significantly%20since%20its%20May%20IPO%2C%20however.%20The%20company%20boasts%20over%20a%20%243.6%20billion%20market%20cap%20as%20of%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeGagne%20added%20that%20investors%20might%20be%20more%20forgiving%20toward%20unprofitable%20healthcare%20AI%20businesses%20as%20retail%20buyers%20chase%20the%20emerging%20tech's%20growth%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStartups%20in%20hot%20industries%20could%20also%20get%20a%20boost%20in%20their%20IPO%20timelines%2C%20DeGagne%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-ozempic-leading-ipo-omada-health-latest-growth-surge-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOmada%20Health's%20obesity%20care%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20surged%20as%20prescriptions%20for%20weight-loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20continue%20to%20climb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStowe%20said%20Hinge%20Health's%20and%20Omada%20Health's%20IPOs%20send%20positive%20signals%20for%20the%20IPO%20market%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20startups%20decide%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20opening%20right%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20is%20pretty%20robust.%20It's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20for%20all%20companies%2C%20but%20conditions%20feel%20as%20strong%20as%20I've%20seen%20them%20in%20a%20while%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20near%20term%2C%20at%20least%20until%20we%20get%20another%20macro%20shock%2C%20you've%20got%20the%20right%20backdrop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-expect-digital-health-startups-rush-to-ipo-this-year-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750928401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685b02793d5881a51c1c01a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-expect-digital-health-startups-rush-to-ipo-this-year-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hinge%20Health%20and%20Omada%20Health%20reawakened%20the%20digital%20health%20IPO%20market.%20But%20most%20late-stage%20healthcare%20startups%20aren't%20ready%20to%20follow%20them%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rtorrence%40businessinsider.com%20(Rebecca%20Torrence)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdont-expect-digital-health-startups-rush-to-ipo-this-year-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20finance%20industry's%20newest%20social%20media%20sensation%20roasts%20private%20equity%20bros%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20they%20love%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223006%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20makes%20funny%20faces%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c586b85e81483682cc4ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223893%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohnny%20Hilbrant%20Partridge%3Cp%3ESimon%20Simard%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJohnny%20Hilbrant%20Partridge's%20parody%20of%20private%20equity%20is%20making%20a%20splash%20on%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20sat%20down%20with%20the%20fitness%20instructor%20about%20where%20he%20gets%20his%20ideas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20hats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he's%20been%20invited%20to%20perform%20as%20%26quot%3BPE%20guy%26quot%3B%20for%20finance%20firms%20and%20business%20schools.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjohnnyhilbrant%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPE%20guy%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20spring%20while%20aimlessly%20scrolling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-instagram-meme-empire-doing-things-strategy-dms-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInstagram%20Reels%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20recognized%20the%20character%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20a%20structured%20hat%20and%20a%20vest%20or%20golf%20polo%2C%20PE%20guy%20corners%20his%20viewers%20with%20an%20awkward%20stream%20of%20casual%20brags%20about%20the%20many%20status%20symbols%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-salaries-at-blackstone-apollo-kkr-bain-others%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bsubstantial%26quot%3B%20pay%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20affords%20him%3A%20luxury%20vacations%2C%20posh%20zip%20codes%2C%20country%20clubs%2C%20and%20private%20schooling%20for%20his%20three%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20found%20the%20character%20a%20little%20too%20annoying%20and%20scrolled%20past%2C%20but%20he%20kept%20popping%20up%20in%20my%20feed%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20I%20was%20hooked.%20So%20hooked%20that%20my%20wife%20has%20banned%20me%20from%20starting%20sentences%20with%20PE%20guy's%20%26quot%3Bnnn%20yeah%26quot%3B%20vocal%20tic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%2C%20I%20wasn't%20the%20only%20one%20who%20couldn't%20look%20away.%20Private%20equity%20professionals%20I%20follow%20on%20Instagram%20were%20liking%20his%20videos%20before%20I%20could%20watch%20them%2C%20and%20he%20dominated%20the%20conversation%20at%20a%20recent%20breakfast%20I%20had%20with%20a%20public%20relations%20professional%20who%20works%20with%20the%20industry.%20To%20gut%20check%20my%20hunch%2C%20I%20texted%20a%20trusted%20industry%20executive%20who%20forwarded%20me%20a%20screenshot%20of%20his%20group%20chat%20with%20other%20insiders%20espousing%20their%20love%20of%20the%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20clear.%20I%20had%20to%20speak%20to%20PE%20guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnny%20Hilbrant%20Partridge%20is%20a%2035-year-old%20Boston-based%20fitness%20instructor%20with%20no%20financial%20industry%20experience.%20He%20said%20his%20portrayal%20of%20a%20wealthy%20professional%20stuck%20in%20a%20bubble%20has%20struck%20a%20chord%20beyond%20Wall%20Street%2C%20resonating%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-tiktok-wall-street-revival-tech-bro-cool-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20who've%20dated%20finance%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20workers%20whose%20companies%20they%20have%20acquired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20Instagram%20following%20has%20grown%20to%2090%2C000%2C%20up%20from%20under%2010%2C000%20since%20the%20character%20debuted%20in%20March.%20And%20it's%20led%20to%20a%20flood%20of%20requests%20for%20personalized%20video%20messages%20via%20the%20Cameo%20app%20and%20other%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20our%20conversation%20with%20Partridge%2C%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%2C%20on%20how%20he%20came%20up%20with%20PE%20guy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-investing-billions-into-restaurants-fast-casuals-boom-bust-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehis%20take%20on%20private%20equity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20why%20he's%20been%20reluctant%20to%20accept%20performance%20offers%20from%20PE%20firms%20and%20college%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224373%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johnny%20Hilbrant%20Patridge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c5df685e81483682cc5c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatridge%20filming%20at%20home%3Cp%3ESimon%20Simard%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20me%20a%20bit%20about%20yourself%20and%20the%20impetus%20for%20PE%20guy.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20making%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20since%20you%20could%20put%20videos%20on%20Instagram.%20My%20goal%20has%20always%20been%20to%20make%20people%20laugh.%20I%20made%20fun%20of%20a%20Midwest%20mom%20who%20is%20basically%20my%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPE%20guy%20came%20from%20talking%20to%20people%20at%20weddings%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20self-awareness.%20At%20every%20wedding%20I've%20been%20to%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20I've%20been%20stuck%20with%20somebody%20talking%20at%20me%20about%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20fitness%20instructor%20and%20I've%20never%20worked%20in%20finance%2C%20but%20I%20have%20an%20undergraduate%20business%20degree%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20peers%20are%20in%20banking%20or%20finance.%20Some%20of%20these%20people%20love%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20jobs%20and%20use%20acronyms%20I%20don't%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20conversation%2C%20they%20will%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20it%20you%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20When%20I%20say%20I'm%20a%20fitness%20instructor%2C%20their%20heads%20almost%20explode%20because%20they%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20relate%20to%20this%20person.%20Sometimes%2C%20they'll%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20your%20company%20private%20equity%20backed%3F%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20last-ditch%20effort%20to%20find%20some%20sort%20of%20common%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20an%20annoying%20wedding%20conversation%20turn%20into%20PE%20guy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20mention%20of%20PE%20was%20in%20a%20video%20where%20the%20character%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20your%20company%20PE-backed%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20based%20on%20a%20real%20conversation.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20if%20my%20company%20was%20PE-backed%2C%20and%20I%20was%20made%20to%20feel%20like%20I%20should%20know%20that%2C%20and%20that%20private%20equity%20is%20the%20be-all%20end-all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20that%20character%20morphed%20into%20the%20PE%20guy%2C%20who%20loves%20to%20talk%20about%20his%20wifey%2C%20which%20is%20hilarious%20to%20me.%20I'm%20married%20to%20a%20man.%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20kids%2C%20but%20PE%20guy%20suddenly%20had%20a%20son%20named%20Tarantino%2C%20which%20people%20loved.%20So%20then%20I%20added%20two%20daughters%20(Montauk%20and%20EBITDA)%2C%20and%20then%20I%20just%20revealed%20in%20a%20video%20that%20wifey's%20pregnant%20with%20a%20fourth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20definitely%20a%20lack%20of%20continuity.%20Sometimes%2C%20people%20will%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20you%20said%20Tarantino%20plays%20squash.%20How%20come%20he%20plays%20soccer%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20But%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20things%20are%20just%20happy%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20the%20character%20have%20a%20name%3F%20Or%20is%20he%20just%20PE%20guy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20have%20a%20name.%20I%20don't%20know%20that%20he%20will%20ever%20have%20a%20name%2C%20because%20then%20there's%20going%20to%20be%20someone%20named%20Shane%20who's%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20don't%20use%20that%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20kind%20of%20a%20weird%20mystique%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20a%20name%2C%20and%20that%20you've%20never%20seen%20his%20wife.%20People%20will%20comment%20that%20they%20want%20to%20see%20wifey.%20I'm%20never%20going%20to%20do%20that%20%E2%80%94%20unless%20a%20year%20from%20now%20I%20decide%20to%20get%20a%20mask%20and%20wig%20to%20look%20like%20wifey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20reaction%20have%20you%20had%20from%20the%20industry%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20some%20PE%20firms%20and%20other%20financial%20businesses%20reach%20out%20to%20me%20to%20perform.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20that%2C%20because%20my%20face%20doesn't%20actually%20look%20like%20that%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20recent%20call%20was%20from%20a%20big%20bank.%20The%20person%20said%20their%20managing%20partner%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDo%20whatever%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20PE%20guy%20here%20with%20that%20face.%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20them%20I%20can't%20do%20that%2C%20and%20the%20guy%20suggested%20that%20they%20make%20a%20mask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20are%20loving%20it.%20I've%20made%20250%20personalized%20videos%20in%206%20weeks.%20I%20recently%20launched%20a%20T-shirt%2C%20and%20we're%20making%20a%20hat%20for%20people%20asking%20for%20merch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20really%20surprised%20by%20the%20number%20of%20older%20men%20in%20finance%20who've%20reached%20out.%20I've%20made%20a%20ton%20of%20Cameos%20for%20people's%20retired%20parents.%20A%20friend%20told%20me%20their%20dad%20loves%20my%20videos.%20I've%20had%20people%20tell%20me%20their%20whole%20office%20is%20talking%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224387%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johnny%20Hilbrant%20Patridge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685c5d903d5881a51c1c1699%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223290%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPatridge%20filming%20at%20home%3Cp%3ESimon%20Simard%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou're%20a%20trainer%20at%20Barry's.%20Has%20PE%20guy%20ever%20come%20up%20in%20your%20day%20job%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20will%20come%20up%20to%20me%20and%20say%20they%20work%20with%20people%20like%20this.%20Or%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20god%2C%20this%20is%20my%20husband.%20He%20always%20talks%20about%20his%20Rolex.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20hasn't%20come%20up%20negatively%20in%20any%20way%2C%20even%20for%20the%20business%20itself.%20Barry's%20is%20owned%20by%20private%20equity%2C%20and%20I%20haven't%20gotten%20in%20any%20trouble%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPE%20guy%20is%20incredibly%20braggadocious%20and%20smug.%20Is%20there%20a%20broader%20critique%20of%20the%20industry%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20may%20have%20been%20a%20subconscious%20critique%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20set%20out%20to%20call%20anyone%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20is%20an%20oral%20surgeon.%20He%20previously%20worked%20at%20a%20private%20practice%20that%20was%20purchased%20by%20a%20private%20equity%20company%2C%20and%20I%20heard%20firsthand%20how%20this%20was%20affecting%20the%20staff%20and%20the%20surgeons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20since%20learned%20that%20private%20equity%20has%20its%20paws%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20things.%20I've%20seen%20it%20with%20different%20businesses%20and%20products%20that%20I%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I've%20learned%20more%2C%20I've%20wondered%20if%20this%20was%20a%20subconscious%20thing%20for%20me.%20Without%20being%20like%20%26quot%3Beat%20the%20rich%2C%26quot%3B%20I'm%20learning%20that%20people%20feel%20like%20private%20equity%20is%20removing%20the%20middle%20class%20in%20this%20country.%20It%20wasn't%20intentional%2C%20but%20it%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20vent%20sesh%20about%20the%20state%20of%20business%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHave%20you%20heard%20from%20anyone%20offended%20by%20PE%20guy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20probably%20people%20who%20work%20in%20private%20equity%20who%20see%20it%20and%20think%20it's%20not%20funny.%20But%20so%20far%2C%20knock%20on%20wood%2C%20no%20one%20has%20felt%20hurt%20enough%20to%20reach%20out%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20hurting%20our%20feelings%2C%20or%20you're%20hurting%20my%20managing%20partner's%20feelings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20more%20like%20women%20reaching%20out%20and%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20literally%20my%20ex.%20Do%20you%20know%20him%20by%20chance%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20that%20someone%20who's%20like%20the%20character%20would%20not%20find%20it%20funny%2C%20but%20I%20haven't%20heard%20from%20them.%20And%20if%20they%20feel%20like%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20me%3F%26quot%3B%20maybe%20I'm%20making%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place.%20Maybe%20next%20time%20they're%20at%20a%20wedding%2C%20they%20won't%20ram%20that%20stuff%20down%20someone's%20throat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20speaking%20to%20someone%20in%20PE%20who%20was%20wondering%20how%20you%20get%20your%20specific%20references%2C%20especially%20for%20your%20city%20videos.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20I%20picked%20cities%20where%20I%20had%20friends.%20Some%20of%20my%20friends'%20husbands%20work%20in%20PE.%20I'd%20also%20Google%20things%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20most%20expensive%20country%20club%20in%20San%20Francisco%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20misses%20here%20or%20there%2C%20and%20people%20would%20comment%3A%20%26quot%3BYou'd%20never%20go%20to%20Wee%20Burn%20Country%20Club%20if%20you%20lived%20in%20Greenwich.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20it's%20crowdsourced.%20I'm%20not%20even%20asking%20for%20it%2C%20but%20people%20will%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20if%20you%20do%20Nashville%2C%20include%20this%2C%20this%2C%20and%20this.%26quot%3B%20They'll%20send%20me%20three%20paragraphs%20of%20stuff.%20I'm%20working%20on%20Nashville%20later%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet's%20discuss%20the%20face%20filter.%20I'll%20be%20honest%3A%20The%20first%20time%20I%20saw%20it%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20real.%20Can%20you%20tell%20me%20how%20you%20landed%20on%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20an%20iguana%2C%20and%20someone%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BThat's%20actually%20the%20North%20American%20whatever%20Iguana%2C%20and%20they're%20known%20for%20swimming.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20used%20this%20filter%20to%20make%20a%20video%20making%20fun%20of%20that%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Iguana%20video%2C%20I%20kept%20using%20that%20filter%20to%20play%20know-it-alls%2C%20which%20eventually%20morphed%20into%20PE%20Guy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johnny%20Hilbrant%20Patridge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20sr