ning%20out%2C%20a%20quiet%20farming%20revolution%20is%20taking%20root%20%E2%80%94%20right%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20backyards%20and%20terraces.%C2%A0%20Aquaponics%20is%20an%20innovative%20farming%20technique%20that%20integrates%20hydroponics%20and%20aquaculture%2C%20enabling%20the%20simultaneous%20cultivation%20of%20fish%20and%20plants%20using%20minimal%20resources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20system%2C%20plants%20are%20grown%20in%20water%20while%20fish%20are%20raised%20in%20the%20same%20or%20interconnected%20systems.%20The%20process%20is%20self-sustaining%3A%20the%20fish%20are%20fed%2C%20and%20their%20waste%20provides%20essential%20nutrients%20for%20the%20plants%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20chemical%20fertilisers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20highly%20organic%20approach%20offers%20the%20added%20benefit%20of%20dual%20income%2C%20as%20both%20fish%20and%20plants%20can%20be%20harvested.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20guide%20offers%20tips%20on%20setting%20up%20a%20commercial%20aquaponics%20farm%2C%20covering%20crucial%20aspects%20such%20as%20setup%20processes%2C%20costs%2C%20fertilisation%2C%20pH%20and%20temperature%20management%2C%20and%20water%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20How%20much%20space%20do%20you%20need%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kerala-based%20farmer%20Vijayakumar%20Narayanan%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299137%2Fkerala-farmer-aquaponics-farming-fish-vegetables-earns-in-lakhs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CTo%2520put%2520together%2520an%2520aquaponics%2Cchoice%252C%2520especially%2520for%2520a%2520beginner.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_