20the%20fish's%20stomach%20%E2%80%94%20and%20documents%20handwritten%20by%20Leonardo%20da%20Vinci%20as%20wedding%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOftentimes%2C%20the%20gift%20holds%20some%20sort%20of%20sentimental%20value%20%E2%80%94%20a%20customized%20padel%20racket%20for%20your%20billionaire%20padel%20partner%2C%20Chesterfield%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%2C%20he%20added%2C%20has%20less%20to%20do%20with%20heartfelt%20admiration%20and%20more%20to%20do%20with%20ego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20this%20kind%20of%20fear%20for%20these%20people%20who%20are%20below%20that%20tier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20gift%20givers.%20%26quot%3BThey%20just%20want%20to%20be%20remembered%20at%20a%20really%20important%20VIP%20wedding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20gift%20options%20could%20include%20commissioned%20art%20that%20features%20the%20couple's%20home%20or%20wedding%20venue%2C%20or%20a%20rare%2C%20first-edition%20print%20of%20a%20book%20that%20aligns%20with%20their%20interests%2C%20according%20to%20Roberta%20Camille%20Lione%2C%20a%20luxury%20wedding%20planner%20and%20founder%20of%20Italian%20Knot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20ideas%20that%20would%20be%20especially%20fitting%20for%20Bezos%20and%20S%C3%A1nchez%2C%20Billy%20Folchetti%2C%20the%20luxury%20wedding%20planner%20and%20founder%20of%20Luxe%2C%20said%20a%20rare%20timepiece%20would%20be%20great%20for%20Bezos%2C%20a%20known%20watch%20enthusiast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20a%20group%20of%20guests%20could%20go%20in%20on%20purchasing%20the%20rights%20to%20name%20several%20stars%20for%20the%20couple%2C%20gifting%20the%20space-exploring%20newlyweds%20their%20own%20constellation.%20The%20name%20wouldn't%20be%20officially%20recognized%20by%20a%20government%20body%2C%20but%20could%20be%20a%20nice%20sentimental%20gesture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20famous%20friends%20of%20Bezos%20and%20S%C3%A1nchez%20could%20lean%20on%20their%20talents%20and%20create%20an%20original%20song%20about%20their%20love%20st