tle%22%3A%22Welcome%20to%20the%20age%20of%20invite%20overload%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20mailbox%20holding%20a%20phone%20with%20an%20E-vite%20on%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6859a3d785e81483682c95f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJulia%20Landon%20is%20moving%20out%20of%20Jersey%20City%20this%20summer%2C%20and%20she's%20enlisting%20her%20friends%20to%20schlep%20boxes.%20Instead%20of%20texting%20or%20calling%20them%20to%20beg%20for%20help%2C%20she's%20inviting%20them%20on%20Partiful.%20The%2027-year-old%20made%20three%20events%20on%20the%20popular%20event%20planning%20app%3A%20one%20for%20packing%20(%26quot%3BPizza%2C%20Packing%20and%20Party%20%E2%80%94%20oh%20my!%26quot%3B)%2C%20one%20for%20loading%20the%20truck%20(marked%20with%20a%20cartoon%20of%20a%20vintage%20U-Haul%20truck%20that%20reads%20%26quot%3BU%20help%20me%20haul%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20company's%20logo)%2C%20and%20a%20final%20going%20away%20party%20at%20a%20bar%20(%26quot%3BOne%20Last%20Time%2C%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20because%20no%20Gen%20Z%20party%20is%20complete%20without%20one%2C%20is%20decked%20with%20a%20Shrek%20meme).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202020%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandreessen-horowitz-benchmark-partiful-event-startup-tech-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eventure-backed%20Partiful%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20become%20the%20talk%20of%20the%20town%20in%20online%20invites%20and%20is%20trying%20to%20grow%20beyond%20the%20casual%20hang%20to%20take%20on%20save%20the%20dates%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-share-best-and-worst-wedding-trends-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewedding%20invites%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20it's%20competing%20in%20a%20crowded%20marketplace%20of%20companies%20looking%20to%20get%20ROI%20from%20your%20RSVP.%20There's%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-invites-app-competes-partiful-rival-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Invites%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Shine%20Parties%20(from%20former%20Yahoo%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarissa-mayer-sunshine-yahoo-ceo-ai-2024-forecast-2023-12%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMarissa%2520Mayer%2520is%2520the%2520cofounder%2C%252C%2520%2522Looking%2520Ahead%25202024.%2522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarissa%20Mayer's%20AI%20company%20Sunshine%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20also%20Luma%2C%20all%20of%20which%20echo%20Partiful's%20playful%20vibe.%20There%20are%20early%20adopters%20like%20Evite%20and%20Paperless%20Post%2C%20which%20are%20known%20for%20email%20invitations%20more%20than%20texts.%20And%20then%20there's%20a%20chaotic%20flurry%20of%20other%20ways%20to%20ask%20people%20to%20come%20to%20your%20hang%3A%20group%20chats%2C%20email%20threads%2C%20Instagram%20close%20friends%20stories%2C%20Snapchats%2C%20Canva%20cards%2C%20and%20the%20dying%20art%20of%20a%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20phones%20endlessly%20ping%20with%20invites%2C%20it's%20harder%20to%20understand%20what%20we're%20attending%20and%20what's%20expected%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELandon%20says%20using%20Partiful%20%26quot%3Breally%20does%20help%20set%20the%20tone%26quot%3B%20of%20whatever%20event%20she's%20hosting%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20party%20or%20a%20Seder.%20The%20app's%20cute%20aesthetic%20leans%20more%20fun%20than%20formal%2C%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20make%20bubbles%20and%20confetti%20move%20across%20the%20screen%20and%20add%20personalized%20GIFs.%20But%20that%20also%20can%20be%20cringe%20to%20older%20invitees%2C%20and%20the%20option%20to%20have%20guests%20Venmo%20funds%20toward%20your%20party%20upon%20RSVP'ing%20could%20send%20most%20over%2040%20into%20an%20etiquette%20tailspin.%20Tech%20should%20have%20made%20invites%20seamless.%20But%20there's%20no%20consensus%20on%20a%20straightforward%2C%20non-cringe%2C%20anxiety-quelling%20way%20to%20earnestly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphones-loneliness-friendship-apps-dating-fatigue-meetups-algorithms-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eask%20people%20to%20show%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20you.%20There%20are%20too%20many%20ways%20to%20send%20invites%20running%20into%20too%20many%20ways%20to%20receive%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ultimately%2C%20some%20people%20will%20still%20ignore%20an%20invite%20or%20choose%20not%20to%20show%20up.%20RSVP%20etiquette%20seems%20to%20have%20died%20off%20just%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-love-to-cancel-plans-friends-bad-health-society-economy-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflaking%20has%20risen%20to%20a%20social%20norm%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWelcome%20to%20the%20age%20of%20invitation%20overload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20exhausting%2C%26quot%3B%20Fernanda%20Read%20tells%20me%20of%20the%20state%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparent-of-first-grader-experiencing-digital-overload-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvitations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20founder%20of%20the%20luxury%20travel%20company%20At%20The%20Top%20But%20Not%20Alone%20says%20she%20prefers%20%26quot%3Bwhatever%20doesn't%20require%20me%20to%20make%20a%20new%20account.%26quot%3B%20Read%2C%2043%2C%20recently%20received%20a%20wedding%20invite%20in%20a%20group%20text%20and%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20was%20thrown%20into%20a%20sea%20of%20dozens%20of%20unknown%20phone%20numbers.%20That%20wasn't%20any%20better%2C%20she%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20a%20hot%20mess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20I've%20received%20invites%20for%3A%20an%20adult's%20birthday%20party%20in%20a%20vacant%20lot%2C%20replete%20with%20live%20reptiles%2C%20sent%20via%20Partiful%3B%20a%20wedding%20via%20Paperless%20Post%3B%20a%2030th%20birthday%20marked%20with%20a%20Canva-made%20card%20sent%20in%20a%20chatty%20group%20text%20(cute%2C%20but%20I%20made%20the%20mistake%20of%20not%20saving%20the%20image%20and%20struggled%20to%20remember%20what%20time%20dinner%20started)%3B%20and%20a%20barbecue%20using%20Facebook%20that%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20about%20until%20the%20friend%20texted%20me%20a%20few%20days%20before%20wondering%20whether%20I%20was%20coming.%20People%20take%20to%20Reddit%20to%20ask%20repeatedly%20what%20invite%20platforms%20are%20best%20for%20communicating%20across%20groups%2C%20what%20they%20should%20use%20for%20a%20toddler's%20birthday%2C%20or%20whether%20digital%20invites%20for%20a%20wedding%20are%20tacky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20Post%20would%20drop%20an%20f-bomb%20if%20she%20were%20alive%20today%20to%20see%20the%20chaotic%20state%20of%20invitation%20etiquette.%20I%20spoke%20with%20experts%20on%20manners%20and%20invitations%20as%20well%20as%20the%20self-appointed%20event%20coordinators%20of%20their%20friend%20groups%20about%20how%20they%20navigate%20the%20stress%20and%20anxiety%20of%20modern%20party%20planning%20and%20why%20they're%20brave%20enough%20to%20keep%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firl-social-startups-combat-loneliness-among-millennials-gen-z-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einviting%20people%20to%20get%20together%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%20they're%20sent%2C%20all%20invites%20should%20receive%20replies%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20formal%20or%20informal%2C%20says%20Myka%20Meier%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20etiquette%20school%20Beaumont%20Etiquette.%20But%20those%20that%20are%20personalized%20and%20actually%20address%20the%20invitee%2C%20whether%20on%20Evite%20or%20in%20a%20call%20or%20text%2C%20are%20likely%20to%20influence%20the%20receiver%20to%20feel%20their%20presence%20at%20an%20event%20is%20more%20important.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20feel%20like%20there%20was%20little%20effort%20put%20into%20the%20invitation%2C%20you'll%20see%20probably%20little%20effort%20for%20the%20reply%2C%26quot%3B%20Meier%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20an%20invite%20goes%20out%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20small%20detail%2C%20but%20it%20can%20make%20or%20break%20a%20gathering.%20%26quot%3BHow%20you%20communicate%20things%20is%20very%20important%2C%20and%20it%20influences%20what%20the%20person%20understands%20about%20the%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Alexa%20Hirschfeld%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Paperless%20Post%2C%20which%20has%20sent%20nearly%20a%20billion%20invites%20since%202009%20and%20focuses%20on%20more%20formal%20events%2C%20like%20weddings%2C%20showers%2C%20and%20milestone%20birthdays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20dawn%20of%20online%20invitations%20some%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20we've%20made%20the%20invite%20process%20messier.%20Various%20invite%20companies%20may%20encourage%20people%20to%20download%20apps%3B%20Partiful%20prompts%20guests%20to%20RSVP%20before%20revealing%20the%20event's%20location%20or%20other%20attendees%20(which%20can%20leave%20hosts%20with%20handfuls%20of%20maybes%2C%20a%20Type%20A%20planner's%20nightmare).%20New%20York%20Tech%20Week%20caused%20drama%20earlier%20this%20month%20by%20requiring%20all%20official%20events%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa16z-partiful-invites-stirs-drama-new-york-tech-week-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euse%20Partiful%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%2C%20which%20ran%20the%20latest%20iteration%20of%20Tech%20Week%2C%20is%20also%20an%20investor%20in%20Partiful%2C%20leading%20the%20app's%20%2420%20million%20Series%20A%20in%202022.%20The%20move%20left%20Tech%20Week%20attendees%20confused%20about%20whether%20they%20should%20look%20to%20Luma%20or%20Partiful%20for%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20%26quot%3Bstrayed%20from%20the%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20planning%2C%20says%20Tyler%20Bainbridge%2C%20a%20former%20software%20engineer%20at%20Meta%20who's%20the%2029-year-old%20founder%20of%20the%20new%20social%20network%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPI.FYI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPI.FYI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20many%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-dismissed-concerns-users-leaving-meta-platforms-virtue-signaling-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabandoned%20their%20Facebook%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there's%20been%20nothing%20like%20the%20site's%20events%20feature%20to%20help%20people%20discover%20events%20as%20seamlessly%20%E2%80%94%20Bainbridge%20says%20he'll%20often%20see%20a%20post%20on%20Instagram%20for%20an%20event%20and%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20looks%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20it's%20easily%20lost.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20actually%20see%20which%20of%20your%20friends%20are%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BThey%20may%20have%202%2C000%20likes%2C%20but%20who's%20actually%20going%20to%20the%20thing%3F%20And%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20forget%20about%20them.%26quot%3B%20He%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPI.FYI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPI.FYI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20working%20on%20its%20own%20events%20feature%2C%20which%20would%20draw%20people%20more%20to%20community%20events%20they%20have%20an%20interest%20in%2C%20much%20like%20Facebook%20has%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20younger%20hosts%2C%20Partiful%20is%20the%20standout%20replacement.%20Kirsten%20Meyer%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20in%20Portland%2C%20Oregon%20who%20works%20in%20public%20relations%2C%20swears%20by%20the%20app%20to%20send%20out%20invites%20even%20when%20a%20gathering%20includes%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20people.%20(On%20TikTok%2C%20people%20make%20videos%20about%20asking%20someone%20on%20a%20date%20via%20Partiful%20or%20setting%20up%20time%20for%20crash-out%20convos%20with%20a%20bestie.)%20She's%20hosted%20a%20murder-mystery-themed%20party%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BLove%20Island%26quot%3B%20watch%20party%2C%20and%20a%20Beer%20Olympics.%20Customizing%20the%20invites%20instead%20of%20just%20sending%20a%20text%2C%20she%20says%2C%20helps%20%26quot%3Bto%20get%20the%20vibe%20and%20theme%20across%26quot%3B%20and%20conveys%20that%20people%20better%20come%20prepared%20to%20play%20their%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartiful%20declined%20to%20share%20specific%20numbers%20on%20invites%20with%20me%2C%20but%20Jess%20Eames%2C%20head%20of%20the%20company's%20business%20and%20product%20operations%2C%20tells%20me%20in%20an%20email%20that%20Partiful%20has%20hosted%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20invites.%20Birthdays%20are%20popular%2C%20but%20so%20is%20%26quot%3Bthrowing%20parties%20without%20any%20particular%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20partying%2C%26quot%3B%20Eames%20says%2C%20and%20weddings%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%20on%20the%20app%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvites%20matter%2C%20but%20maybe%20the%20platforms%20they're%20sent%20on%20don't.%20Sukhi%20Sahni%20takes%20party%20planning%20so%20seriously%20that%20her%20friends%20have%20jokingly%20dubbed%20her%20the%20chief%20administrative%20officer%20of%20her%20WhatsApp%20chat%2C%20the%20NOVA%20gang%20(short%20for%20Northern%20Virginia%2C%20where%20she%20and%20a%20few%20other%20longtime%20friends%20live).%20She%20has%20hosted%20big%20events%20like%20Christmas%20and%20Diwali%20celebrations%2C%20but%20she%20also%20helps%20make%20personalized%20invites%20for%20different%20members%20of%20the%20group's%20birthdays%2C%20sometimes%20sending%20out%20videos%20that%20feature%20photos%20of%20the%20honoree%20and%20include%20a%20voice%20memo%20at%20the%20end%20with%20the%20pertinent%20details.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20yourself%20in%20something%2C%20you%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20connect%2C%26quot%3B%20Sahni%2C%20a%20public%20relations%20marketing%20executive%2C%20tells%20me.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20group%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20big%20milestone%3A%20Several%20members%20are%20turning%2050.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20lead%20up%20to%20the%20event%20%E2%80%94%20Sahni%20tells%20me%20she%20will%20also%20often%20take%20the%20photos%20from%20the%20event%20and%20turn%20them%20into%20a%20picture%20book%20as%20a%20gift.%20Part%20of%20what%20makes%20these%20events%20so%20successful%20is%20that%20people%20trust%20that%20when%20Sahni%20is%20behind%20the%20planning%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20turn%20out%20well.%20That%20meant%20building%20trust%20over%20multiple%20gatherings%20and%20sending%20people%20nudges%20and%20reminders%20to%20set%20expectations%20about%20RSVP'ing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHosting%20for%20big%20groups%20in%202025%20means%20fighting%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fghosting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enorm%20of%20ghosting%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cancelling%20plans.%20Some%20have%20given%20up%20on%20nailing%20down%20the%20head%20count.%20Tom%20O'Malley%2C%20a%2040-year-old%20in%20Springfield%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20is%20in%20159%20group%20chats%20%E2%80%94%20some%20with%20friends%2C%20but%20many%20with%20parents%20from%20his%20kids'%20school%20or%20soccer%20club.%20His%20family%20hosts%20two%20large%20get-togethers%20a%20year%20(for%20back%20to%20school%20and%20St.%20Patrick's%20Day)%20and%20smaller%20ones%20monthly.%20O'Malley%20tells%20me%20his%20wife%20will%20make%20an%20invite%20card%20on%20Canva%20and%20then%20email%20it%20to%20some%20people%20and%20text%20blast%20it%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20good%20way%20to%20track%20who%20is%20coming%20with%20that%20method%2C%20but%20O'Malley%20has%20found%20that%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20Yes%2C%20some%20people%20who%20RSVP%20don't%20turn%20up%20anyway%2C%20leaving%20his%20family%20with%20too%20much%20leftover%20food%20and%20beer.%20But%20now%2C%20O'Malley%20takes%20more%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bthrow%20it%20out%20there%20and%20see%20what%20happens%26quot%3B%20approach.%20Despite%20people%20being%20flaky%2C%20he%20says%2C%20those%20who%20have%20shown%20up%20have%20a%20new%20look%20on%20gathering%20and%20may%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20come%20back.%20%26quot%3BI%20forgot%20that%20this%20was%20super%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%20some%20people%20have%20told%20him.%20By%20letting%20go%20of%20anxiety%20around%20hosting%20and%20high%20expectations%20of%20others%2C%20he's%20been%20liberated%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20him%20a%20more%20relaxed%20host%20and%20the%20parties%20more%20enjoyable.%20%26quot%3BTo%20be%20the%20kind%20of%20social%20beacon%20to%20some%20degree%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20kind%20of%20just%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20planning%20a%20birthday%20party%20for%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month%2C%20a%20task%20I%20find%20increasingly%20embarrassing%20as%20a%20person%20fully%20in%20my%2030s%20still%20desperately%20awaiting%20RSVPs.%20I%20defaulted%20to%20Partiful%2C%20as%20it%20seemed%20the%20method%20my%20different%20groups%20of%20friends%20would%20all%20be%20most%20likely%20to%20use%2C%20and%20I%20was%20happy%20it%20took%20on%20the%20task%20of%20sending%20nudges%20to%20invited%20guests%20to%20commit%20and%20reminders%20to%20show%20up.%20Despite%20sending%20out%20the%20invite%20weeks%20in%20advance%20for%20a%20Sunday%20afternoon%20hang%2C%20I'm%20dealing%20with%20an%20accordion%20effect%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20attendees%3B%20the%20numbers%20rise%20and%20fall%20as%20people%20change%20their%20plans%2C%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%26quot%3B%20replies%20taunt%20me%2C%20sparking%20an%20internal%20debate%20as%20to%20whether%20I%20should%20splurge%20for%20a%20bigger%20reservation%20(logically%2C%20I%20know%20that%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%26quot%3B%20probably%20means%20%26quot%3Bno%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20may%20end%20up%20with%20fewer%20guests%20and%20extra%20money%20on%20the%20tab%20that%20leaves%20me%20bitter%20on%20a%20day%20that's%20meant%20to%20be%20fun%20specifically%20for%20me).%20In%20my%20nightmares%2C%20everyone%20flakes%2C%20and%20I'm%20left%20at%20the%20roller%20rink%20alone.%20But%20I'm%20trying%20to%20take%20some%20advice%20and%20optimism%20from%20the%20star%20hosts%20I%20spoke%20with%20for%20this%20story%3A%20plan%20the%20day%2C%20let%20go%2C%20and%20hope%20people%20remember%20that%20it's%20nice%20to%20gather%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-invite-industry-booming-partiful-weddings-apple-hosts-guests-mad-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750925222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6859a3f33d5881a51c1be744%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-invite-industry-booming-partiful-weddings-apple-hosts-guests-mad-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Partiful%2C%20Apple%20Invites%2C%20Paperless%20Post%3A%20How%20online%20invites%20became%20a%20splintered%20mess%20that%20is%20leaving%20hosts%20and%20guests%20in%20a%20bind.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-invite-industry-booming-partiful-weddings-apple-hosts-guests-mad-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20fraud%20detection%20system%20shielded%203.5%20mn%20users%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20says%20Airtel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750924651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%