%20social%20experience%2C%20the%20networking%3F%20And%20then%2C%20looking%20at%20the%20ones%20where%20it%20would%20come%20with%20a%20hundred%20thousand%20dollars%20a%20year%20price%20tag%2C%20do%20those%20really%20make%20sense%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e4b6f1b-8154-406a-9a78-ac9a8b43c641%5C%22%3E'I%20want%20to%20do%20the%20same%20for%20my%20kids'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Susie%20Ha's%20top%20priorities%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20ensuring%20that%20her%20three%20kids%20have%20enough%20money%20saved%20by%20the%20time%20they%20reach%20college%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHa%20and%20her%20husband%20both%20have%20advanced%20degrees%20in%20technology%20and%20engineering%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20she%20said%20that%20she%20wants%20her%20kids%20to%20have%20the%20same%20educational%20opportunities%20that%20she%20had%20to%20help%20them%20be%20successful%20later%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20we%20made%20a%20decent%20income%20and%20had%20multiple%20kids%2C%20that%20just%20got%20me%20thinking%2C%20'Wow%2C%20I%20have%20to%20be%20really%20strategic%20about%20my%20investments%20and%20savings%20if%20we%20want%20our%20kids%20to%20get%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20that%20we%20got%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ha%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20both%20very%20advanced%20degrees.%20We%20were%20lucky%20that%20we%20didn't%20have%20any%20loans%20for%20it%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20do%20the%20same%20for%20my%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20mortgage%20payments%20and%20high%20childcare%20costs%2C%20Ha%20said%20she%20doesn't%20feel%20rich%2C%20and%20at%20times%2C%20feels%20financially%20strained%20despite%20a%20combined%20income%20with%20her%20husband%20in%20the%20low%20six%20figures.%20Before%20having%20her%20third%20child%20this%20year%2C%20Ha%20said%20she%20was%20putting%20about%20%24500%20every%20month%20into%20her%20kids'%20college%20savings.%20With%20high%20childcare%20costs%2C%20she%20said%20she'll%20likely%20decrease%20tha