icleshow%2F122084770.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musks-spacex-faces-legal-threat-from-mexican-president-over-rocket-debris-and-pollution%2Famp_articleshow%2F122084770.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musks-spacex-faces-legal-threat-from-mexican-president-over-rocket-debris-and-pollution%2Famp_articleshow%2F122084770.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Louis%20Vuitton%20traded%20drama%20for%20quiet%20luxury%20with%20Pharrell%20Williams'%20latest%20menswear%20line%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Models%20wear%20creations%20as%20part%20of%20the%20men's%20Louis%20Vuitton%20Spring-Summer%202026%20collection%2C%20which%20was%20presented%20in%20Paris%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20June%2024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685cafed85e81483682cc90e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22671%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPharrell%20Williams'%20new%20menswear%20line%20for%20Louis%20Vuitton%20is%20quiet%20and%20understated.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FMichel%20Euler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELouis%20Vuitton's%20new%20menswear%20line%2C%20designed%20by%20Pharrell%20Williams%2C%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20collections%20of%20old.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20line%2C%20characterized%20by%20neutral%20tones%20and%20simple%2C%20tailored%20silhouettes%2C%20exudes%20quiet%20luxury.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20might%20be%20just%20what%20LVMH%20needs%20to%20help%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20luxury%20slump.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGone%20are%20flashy%20colors%20and%20logos%20%E2%80%94%20Louis%20Vuitton%20unveiled%20its%20new%20men's%20line%20in%20all%20its%20neutral-toned%2C%20quiet%20luxury%20glory%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20Tuesday%20in%20Paris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fashion%20house's%20spring-summer%202026%20collection%20comprised%2060%20looks%3A%20button-downs%2C%20tailored%20blazers%2C%20formal%20pants%2C%20and%20denim%20jackets.%20Most%20were%20in%20earth-toned%20brown%2C%20black%2C%20and%20terracotta%20colors%2C%20with%20pops%20of%20blue%20and%20yellow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stage%2C%20created%20by%20the%20Indian%20architecture%20firm%20Studio%20Mumbai%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eresembled%20a%20magnified%20version%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BSnakes%20and%20Ladders%26quot%3B%20game%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigned%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharrell-williams-to-head-louis-vuittons-menswear-section-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPharrell%20Williams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Louis%20Vuitton's%20men's%20creative%20director%20since%202023%2C%20the%20collection%20is%20a%20departure%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20louder%2C%20more%20avant-garde%20spring-summer%20collections%20of%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrevious%20spring%20collections%20leaned%20heavily%20on%20spectacle%E2%80%94too%20many%20bags%2C%20logos%2C%20and%20runway%20theatrics.%20Here%2C%20Pharrell%20traded%20that%20for%20clarity%20and%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniel%20Langer%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20luxury%20strategy%20at%20Pepperdine%20University%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Louis%20Vuitton%20creative%20told%20GQ%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWilliams%20channeled%20a%202018%20India%20trip%20into%20the%20collection's%20color%20palette%20and%20silhouettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams'%20new%2C%20wearable%20collection%20comes%20as%20LVMH%2C%20along%20with%20most%20of%20the%20luxury%20industry%2C%20struggles%20to%20recover%20from%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-stocks-chart-shows-bad-year-kering-lvmh-gucci-cartier-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emajor%20sales%20slump%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20industry%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20a%20tough%20macroeconomic%20environment%2C%20weakened%20consumer%20confidence%2C%20lower%20spending%20in%20China%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20a%20shift%20in%20consumer%20preferences%20to%20quiet%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20French%20luxury%20giant%2C%20which%20also%20owns%20Dior%2C%20Givenchy%2C%20and%20Bulgari%2C%20reported%20a%201%25%20revenue%20increase%20in%202024%20compared%20to%202023%2C%20with%20sales%20of%2084.7%20billion%20euros%2C%20or%20about%20%2499.10%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reported%20a%2017%25%20decline%20in%20net%20profits%20in%202024%20compared%20to%20the%20year%20before.%20The%20company's%20stock%20is%20down%20nearly%2035%25%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20LVMH%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d723c9e5-aff2-4bd9-9d91-43925cf3ce9c%5C%22%3ELeaning%20harder%20than%20ever%20into%20quiet%20luxury%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Models%20wearing%20looks%20from%20the%20LV%20menswear%20show%20in%20Paris.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ce4aff748d8c055f46356%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELooks%20from%20the%20Louis%20Vuitton%20spring%20menswear%20show%20in%20Paris%20were%20muted%20and%20simple.%3Cp%3EASSOCIATED%20PRESS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collection%20shows%20Louis%20Vuitton's%20pivot%20to%20quiet%20luxury%2C%20the%20dominant%20consumer%20trend%20characterized%20by%20subtle%2C%20logoless%20designs%2C%20neutral%20colors%2C%20and%20a%20focus%20on%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrands%20that%20have%20long%20channeled%20quiet%20luxury%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhermes-escapes-luxury-industry-slump-lvmh-kering-struggle-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHerm%C3%A8s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20thriving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams'%20new%20collection%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20LVMH%20is%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20steady%20the%20ship%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Albert%20Varkki%2C%20cofounder%20of%20luxury%20leather%20goods%20company%20Von%20Baer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLuxury%20is%20recalibrating%20right%20now.%20The%20era%20of%20logo-heavy%20flash%20is%20fading%2C%20and%20aspirational%20buyers%20are%20looking%20for%20pieces%20that%20feel%20more%20grounded%2C%26quot%3B%20Varkki%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20collection%20hits%20that%20sweet%20spot%3A%20still%20premium%2C%20still%20Vuitton%2C%20but%20without%20the%20shout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELanger%2C%20the%20Pepperdine%20professor%2C%20said%20the%20move%20to%20quiet%20luxury%20is%20%26quot%3Btimely%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20draws%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flvmh-says-the-aspirational-customer-is-suffering-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Easpirational%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20middle-income%20buyers%20wanting%20to%20splurge%20on%20luxury%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPharrell%20is%20tapping%20into%20aspirational%20buyers%20who%20crave%20understated%20elegance%20and%20long-term%20value.%20The%20collection%20is%20clearly%20designed%20to%20reignite%20interest%20among%20aspirational%20consumers%20drawn%20to%20the%20quiet%20luxury%20trend%2C%20Langer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuiet%20luxury%20attracts%20not%20just%20older%2C%20established%20clients%2C%20but%20also%20Gen%20Z%20and%20younger%20millennials%20who%20seek%20authenticity%20over%20extravagance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afb8b8b2-5b2f-4bef-8813-c95e2684ede7%5C%22%3EBut%20some%20think%20the%20term%20'quiet%20luxury'%20needs%20to%20die%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Louis%20Vuittons%20leans%20hard%20into%20quiet%20luxury%2C%20some%20retail%20analysts%20think%20the%20trend%20is%20precisely%20what%20caused%20the%20luxury%20slump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20analysts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%