-stock-biggest-market-cap-microsoft-jensen-huang-shareholder-meeting-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nvidia%20reclinched%20its%20title%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20company%20for%20a%20second%20time%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-stock-biggest-market-cap-microsoft-jensen-huang-shareholder-meeting-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Climatiq%20uses%20AI%20to%20automate%20carbon%20emission%20data.%20See%20the%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20raise%20%2411.6%20million.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222044%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Climatiq%20founders.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685ac38a3d5881a51c1bf8e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClimatiq's%20cofounders%3A%20Hessam%20Lavi%2C%20Isis%20T%20Baulig%2C%20and%20Phillip%20von%20Bierberstein.%3Cp%3EClimatiq.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBerlin%20startup%20Climatiq%20raised%20a%20%2411.6%20million%20Series%20A%20led%20by%20Alstin%20Capital.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EClimatiq's%20AI%20platform%20automates%20carbon%20emissions%20data%20for%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20got%20a%20look%20at%20the%2011-slide%20pitch%20deck%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EClimatiq%2C%20a%20startup%20that's%20built%20an%20AI-enabled%20platform%20for%20companies%20to%20collect%20and%20automate%20their%20carbon%20emission%20data%2C%20has%20secured%20a%20%2411.6%20million%20Series%20A%20led%20by%20Alstin%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Berlin%20startup's%20tool%20analyzes%20everything%20from%20supply%20chain%20data%20to%20purchase%20orders%20to%20calculate%20a%20company's%20scope%203%20emissions%2C%20which%20measure%20its%20indirect%20carbon%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20building%20any%20other%20kind%20of%20software%2C%20there%20are%20existing%20APIs%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20for%20carbon%20emissions.%20So%20we've%20built%20an%20infrastructure%20for%20carbon%20tooling%2C%26quot%3B%20Climatiq's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20Hessam%20Lavi%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScope%203%C2%A0emissions%2C%20which%20typically%20represent%20around%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnormative.io%2Finsight%2Fupstream-downstream-emissions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E90%25%20of%20a%20company's%20carbon%20footprint%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20often%20hard%20to%20reliably%20measure%20because%20they%20are%20collated%20from%20a%20fragmented%20set%20of%20data%20points.%20Climatiq's%20AI%20platform%20automates%20the%20collection%20of%20this%20data%20from%20various%C2%A0sources%2C%20such%20as%20NGOs%2C%20the%20Intergovernmental%20Panel%20on%20Climate%20Change%2C%20and%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20carbon%20metrics%20can%20then%20be%20integrated%20into%20companies'%20emissions%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20need%20for%20a%20trusted%20source%20on%20carbon%20data.%20If%20everyone%20is%20reporting%20data%2C%20how%20do%20you%20have%20confidence%20in%20their%20methodology%3F%20That%20got%20us%20interested%20in%20building%20an%20infrastructure%20platform%20for%20carbon%20accounting%2C%26quot%3B%20Lavi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20are%20required%20to%20calculate%20their%20emissions%20data%20to%20ensure%20they're%20complying%20with%20ESG%20regulations.%20Climatiq%20charges%20clients%2C%20which%20include%20the%20likes%20of%20Celonis%20and%20Siemens%2C%20based%20on%20their%20usage.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELavi%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20feeding%20the%20transport%20records%20of%20a%20freight%20company%20into%20its%20platform.%20%26quot%3BWe%20process%20it%2C%20and%20provide%20a%20carbon%20estimate%20to%20our%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20and%20charge%20for%20that%20API%20request%2C%26quot%3B%20Lavi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20second%20term%20has%20triggered%20a%20wave%20of%20backlash%20against%20ESG%20incentives%2C%20which%20has%20had%20a%20knock-on%20effect%20on%20climate%20startups.%20In%20Q1%2C%20VC%20funding%20into%20climate%20tech%20dried%20up%2050%25%20year-on-year%2C%20per%20PitchBook%20data%2C%20and%20high-profile%20climate%20startups%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-05-21%2Fcarbon-removal-startup-climeworks-is-cutting-22-of-staff%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClimeworks%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20announced%20layoffs%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20this%20environment%2C%20Lavi%20found%20the%20fundraising%20process%20considerably%20more%20difficult%20than%20Climatiq's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpitch-deck-climatiq-the-google-analytics-carbon-accounting-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%245.8%20million%20seed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20much%20tougher%20than%20I%20expected.%20Compared%20to%20our%20pre-seed%20and%20seed%2C%20it's%20definitely%20a%20different%20chaos%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20startup%20spoke%20to%20around%2070%20VCs%20for%20this%20funding%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Series%20A%20was%20led%20by%20Munich-based%20venture%20capital%20firm%20Alstin%20Capital%2C%20with%20backing%20from%20Singular%20and%20Cherry%20Ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cash%20injection%2C%20Climatiq%20plans%20to%20grow%20its%20engineering%20head%20count%20and%20develop%20its%20AI%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20got%20a%20look%20at%20the%2011-slide%20deck%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funds.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Climatiq%20Series%20A%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20