%5C%22%3EKey%20points%20to%20remember%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414458%2Flesser-known-indian-summer-fruits-benefits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJamun%20loves%20the%20sun%20and%20thrives%20in%20full%20sunlight.%3C%2Fa%3E%20To%20ensure%20healthy%20growth%20and%20fruiting%2C%20make%20sure%20your%20plant%20gets%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20of%20direct%20sunlight%20every%20day.%20Shady%20spots%20or%20indoor%20corners%20just%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20%E2%80%94%20it%20needs%20light%20to%20photosynthesize%20efficiently%20and%20produce%20quality%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Soil%20should%20drain%20well%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamun%20trees%20do%20not%20appreciate%20wet%20feet!%20While%20they%20can%20adapt%20to%20different%20soil%20types%2C%20loamy%20or%20sandy-loam%20soil%20with%20good%20drainage%20is%20ideal.%20Waterlogged%20soil%20can%20lead%20to%20root%20rot%20and%20fungal%20infections.%20Mix%20in%20some%20sand%20or%20cocopeat%20if%20your%20garden%20soil%20tends%20to%20retain%20too%20much%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Use%20grafted%20saplings%20for%20faster%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20Jamun%20from%20seed%20is%20possible%20but%20requires%20immense%20patience%2C%20as%20it%20can%20take%20eight%20to%2010%20years%20to%20fruit.%20Grafted%20saplings%2C%20however%2C%20are%20clones%20of%20mature%20trees%20and%20typically%20start%20bearing%20fruit%20in%20just%20four%20to%20five%20years.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20also%20have%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20fruit%20quality%20and%20tree%20size%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Water%20less%2C%20no