.%E2%80%9D%20Due%20to%20her%20age%20and%20blinding%20eye%2C%20she%20could%20not%20fend%20for%20herself%20and%20decided%20to%20jump%20into%20a%20lake%20and%20let%20go%20of%20her%20life.%20Rescued%20by%20police%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20Atchayam%20by%20Naveen%20Kumar.Today%2C%20Rathanammal%20has%20recovered%20from%20the%20trauma%20of%20her%20past%20and%20has%20started%20living%20her%20life..%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20go%20anywhere%20till%20my%20last%20breath%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFunding%20remains%20a%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20What%20you%20can%20do%20to%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20often%20than%20not%2C%20we%20do%20not%20think%20about%20begging%20as%20a%20problem%20that%20is%20facing%20our%20country.%20Nor%20do%20we%20pause%20to%20think%20what%20becomes%20of%20them.%20But%20Naveen%20Kumar%20found%20his%20calling%20in%20transforming%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20destitute%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%2C%20they%20are%20no%20different%20from%20our%20kin%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20Yet%2C%20funding%20has%20been%20a%20problem%20for%20the%20team.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20some%20people%20make%20donations%20seeing%20the%20change%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20make%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20been%20sustainable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20this%20problem%2C%20Atchayam%20developed%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98%3Cstrong%3EMOI%20101%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20Moi%20is%20a%20practice%20of%20giving%20gift%20money%20to%20relatives%20on%20special%20occasions%20like%20weddings%20and%20other%20celebrations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20proverb%20goes%2C%20small%20drops%20make%20an%20ocean.%20A%20small%20contribution%20of%20Rs.101%20can%20transform%20somebody%E2%80%99s%20life%20%E2%80%93%20small%20steps%2C%20huge%20changes!%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20give%20us%20a%20hand%2C%20we%20can%20open%20life%E2%80%99s%20hands%20for%20the%20destitute%2C%E2%80%9D%20say