phies%2Fjoseph-priestley%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Science%20History%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20(R)%3A%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrmarysco.com%2F2014%2F02%2F04%2Frff78-joseph-priestly-discovered-carbonated-water-in-1767%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Dr%20Marys%20Co%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20out%20of%20English%20chemist%20Joseph%20Priestley%E2%80%99s%201767%20watershed%20experiment%20of%20infusing%20water%20with%20carbon%20dioxide%20gas%2C%20carbonated%20water%20was%20commercialised%20by%20the%20brand%20Schweppes%20in%201783.%20The%20bubbled%20bliss%20amassed%20quite%20a%20cult%20following.%20In%20Bombay%2C%20an%20aerated%20water%20factory%2C%20Rogers%20started%20in%201837%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20rising%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoda%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20delayed%2C%20or%20there%20was%20pandemonium%2C%20as%20Ardeshir%20witnessed%20for%20himself%20one%20evening%20when%20he%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20bar%20brawl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20the%20commotion%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mules%20are%20late.%20There%20is%20no%20soda%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20told.%20And%20so%20Ardeshir%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F395076%2Fferns-pickles-pune-nataline-fernandes-jams-squashes-preserves-curry-pastes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20experiment%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20would%20sate%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20soda%20appetite.%20He%20found%20a%20way%20to%20produce%20carbonated%20water.%20Soon%2C%20sugar%20and%20flavour%20found%20their%20way%20into%20the%20drink%2C%20and%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20was%20born%2C%20a%20bottled%20range%20of%20fizzy%20cheer%20that%20even%20predates%20Coca-Cola%2C%20which%2C%20by%20most%20estimates%2C%20was%20invented%20in%201886%20%E2%80%94%20two%20years%20after%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20started%20in%201884%20in%20a%20small%20rented%20barrack%20in%20Pune.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20constant%20on%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20chequered%20dining%20tables%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStorytelling%20and%20a%20penchant%20for%20intrepidity%20run%20in%20the%20family%20DNA%2C%20I%20deduce.%20I%E2%80%99m%20listening%20to%20Marzban%E2%80%99s%20tale%20as%20he%20narrates%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F271527%2Fcentury-old-vadilal-ice-cream-brand-first-to-launch-dollies-cones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat-grandfather%E2%80%99s%20itinerant%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20stories%20are%20juxtaposed%20against%20the%20lores%20of%20the%20Zorastrian%20migration%20following%20the%20Arab%20conquest%20in%20651%20AD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20voice%20assumes%20a%20low%20register%20as%20he%20details%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20escape%20from%20Yazd%20in%20Iran%20to%20Quetta%20(now%20in%20Pakistan)%20to%20Pune%20with%20just%20Rs%208.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20great-grandfather%20was%20quite%20a%20prominent%20person%20in%20his%20village%20of%20Yazd.%20One%20day%2C%20while%20on%20his%20way%20to%20work%20in%20his%20%3Cem%3Esavari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(the%20elite%20would%20ride%20donkeys%20back%20in%20the%20day)%2C%20he%20came%20across%20an%20inebriated%20Muslim%20beggar%20who%20demanded%20he%20get%20down%20from%20the%20donkey%20and%20show%20some%20respect%20to%20him.%E2%80%9D%20Ardeshir%20refused%20to.%20Thus%20followed%20an%20altercation%2C%20which%20ended%20with%20the%20beggar%20being%20hurt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20hurting%20a%20Muslim%20was%20a%20grave%20offence.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarzban%20contextualises%20this%2C%20referencing%20the%20religious%20persecutions%20that%20were%20rampant%20at%20the%20time.%20%E2%80%9CZorastrians%20had%20to%20practice%20their%20faith%20in%20hiding.%20To%20further%20humiliate%20them%2C%20a%20law%20had%20been%20passed%20that%2C%20whatever%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20status%2C%20if%20they%20were%20on%20their%20way%20and%20should%20come%20upon%20a%20Muslim%2C%20they%20had%20to%20get%20off%20their%20%3Cem%3Esafari%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20tip%20their%20hat%20and%20do%20%3Cem%3Esalaam%20%3C%2Fem%3E(offer%20a%20greeting).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArdeshir%20had%20clearly%20flouted%20the%20law.%20Fleeing%20seemed%20the%20only%20solution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20he%20grabbed%20that%20era%E2%80%99s%20equivalent%20of%20Rs%208%20and%20fled%20by%20boat%20out%20of%20Yazd%20to%20a%20place%20called%20Quetta%2C%20where%20his%20aunt%20lived%2C%E2%80%9D%20Marzban%20goes%20on%20to%20detail%20how%20Ardeshir%20detested%20those%20months.%20He%20moved%20once%20more%2C%20this%20time%20with%20his%20sights%20trained%20on%20the%20docks%20of%20Bombay.%20But%20a%20few%20months%20of%20toil%20taught%20him%20this%20was%20not%20his%20cup%20of%20tea.%20He%20moved%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20landed%20in%20Pune%2C%20spotted%20chaos%20unfurling%20at%20one%20of%20the%20bars%2C%20causing%20him%20to%20ideate%20an%20experiment%20that%20gave%20th