Marzban%20pauses%20at%20the%20cliffhanger%20bits%2C%20allowing%20suspense%20to%20hang%20in%20the%20air.%20As%20he%20reveals%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20always%20enjoyed%20a%20good%20story.%20When%20he%20was%20little%2C%20he%E2%80%99d%20often%20concoct%20some%20of%20his%20own%20while%20%E2%80%9Cpolishing%20off%20bottles%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20fizzy%20drinks.%20While%20Ardeshir%20had%20invented%20quite%20a%20few%20classics%2C%20Marzban%E2%80%99s%20dad%20added%20the%20orangeade%2C%20lemonade%2C%20raspberry%20and%20ice%20cream%20soda%20and%20%3Cem%3Eteekha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spicy)%20ginger%20to%20the%20list%20when%20he%20took%20over.%20Marzban%20explains%20that%20while%20his%20father%20took%20charge%20of%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%2C%20his%20uncles%20oversaw%20the%20running%20of%20Frams%20%E2%80%94%20also%20a%20flavoured%20drinks%20business%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20started%20by%20Marzban%E2%80%99s%20grandfather%2C%20Framroze.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20browse%20through%20the%20current%20menu%20at%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20reveals%20a%20caffeine-free%20cola%2C%20peach%2C%20pineapple%2C%20green%20apple%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejeera%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20drink%20featuring%20cumin%20powder)%2C%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20kala%20khatta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(java%20plum%20juice)%20and%20tonic%20water.%20These%20are%20Marzban%E2%80%99s%20innovations%20%E2%80%94%20tradition%20with%20a%20wink%2C%20if%20you%20will.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20yellowing%20recipe%20and%20a%20hefty%20legacy%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%20into%20one%20of%20Pune%E2%80%99s%20Iranian%20eateries%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20spot%20a%20familiar%20silhouette.%20The%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20bottle%20is%20unmistakable.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20weighty%20legacy%20to%20carry%20forward%2C%20Marzban%20learnt%20when%20entrusted%20with%20the%20business%20in%202013%2C%20following%20the%20passing%20of%20his%20father.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20anything%20at%20the%20time.%20How%20do%20I%20make%20the%20flavours%3F%20What%20do%20I%20do%3F%20And%20then%2C%20I%20came%20across%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305528%2Fcookbook-baking-food-history-books-recommended-by-madhur-jaffrey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20old%20yellow%20notebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20my%20father%20had%20scribbled%20down%20the%20formulas%20for%20the%20drink.%20I%20started%20going%20through%20his%20files%2C%20deciphering%20the%20scribbles%2C%20experimenting%2C%20tweaking%20and%20attempting%20to%20do%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20time%20nor%20the%20emergence%20of%20other%20drink%20alternatives%20has%20weathered%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20popularity.%20Marzban%20learnt%20this%20one%20afternoon%2C%20when%20he%20was%20paid%20a%20visit%20by%20an%20elderly%20gentleman%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20%E2%80%9CHe%E2%80%99d%20been%20hunting%20long%20for%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20board%2C%20you%20see.%20Finally%2C%20someone%20told%20him%20where%20he%20could%20find%20the%20%3Cem%3Esodawala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(the%20man%20who%20makes%20sodas)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Marzban%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFwiy7Iiz4I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDFwiy7Iiz4I%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv