les%20are%20returned%20to%20us%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20customer%20is%20only%20paying%20for%20the%20product.%20That%E2%80%99s%20also%20why%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20retail%20across%20India.%20It%E2%80%99s%20because%2C%20if%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20empty%20bottles%20back%20the%20next%20day%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20anything%20to%20fill%20the%20drinks%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20success%20reflected%20in%20its%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20retails%20around%20300%20cases%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20fascinating%20how%20an%20unpredictable%20series%20of%20events%20crescendoed%20into%20giving%20Pune%20its%20favourite%20drink.%20But%20as%20Marzban%20emphasises%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20the%20magic%20of%20old-fashioned%20goodness%20in%20a%20bottle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750649400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fcarbon-dioxide-1-1750417384.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D452524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20predates%20Coca-Cola%2C%20which%2C%20records%20estimate%20to%20be%20an%20invention%20of%201886%20%E2%80%94%20two%20years%20after%20Ardeshir%E2%80%99s%20started%20in%20a%20small%20rented%20barrack%20in%20Pune.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F452524%2Fardeshirs-in-pune-was-started-by-a-zorastrian-immigrant-and-serves-flavoured-soda-drinks%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turn%20Your%20Balcony%20into%20a%20Mini%20Farm%3A%20Grow%20Jackfruit%20with%20Your%20Kids%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWant%20to%20teach%20your%20kids%20sustainability%20and%20the%20joy%20of%20homegrown%20food%3F%20Imagine%20harvesting%20a%20jackfruit%2C%20the%20largest%20fruit%20grown%20in%20India%